data.description: Situated on a large corner lot sits this 4 bedroom/2 bathroom home that features 1,828 square feet of living space with some hardwood flooring, formal dining area, large backyard, and a storage shed/workshop area. This home needs some TLC but is priced to sell and offers a great opportunity for someone looking for a flip property. Contact Colton for any further information!
